description: The suspects allegedly took migrants from France to the UK in refrigerated lorries and rubber boats.
title: Smuggling arrests over transport of '10,000 Kurds' to UK
title_page: Smuggling arrests over transport of '10,000 Kurds' to UK - BBC News
maintext: The group is accused of picking up migrants from car parks in France and taking them to the UK in refrigerated lorries and small rubber boats, law enforcement agency Eurojust said.
